sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Layer
    participant API as NPPP API
    participant Canon as Canonicalization Engine
    participant Bundle as Evidence Bundle Builder
    participant Hash as SHA-256 Hash Engine
    participant Proof as Proof Constructor
    participant GCS as GCS Evidence Storage
    participant Ledger as Proof Ledger Database
    participant Replay as Replay Engine

    Client->>API: Submit artifact for notarization
    API->>Canon: Canonicalize artifact
    Canon->>Bundle: Build deterministic evidence bundle
    Bundle->>Hash: Compute SHA-256
    Hash->>Proof: Construct NPPP proof string
    Proof->>GCS: Store evidence bundle
    Proof->>Ledger: Record proof metadata
    Proof-->>Client: Return proof string + metadata

    Client->>API: Submit proof for verification
    API->>Replay: Start replay verification
    Replay->>GCS: Retrieve bundle
    Replay->>Hash: Recompute SHA-256
    Hash-->>Replay: Computed hash
    Replay-->>API: Comparison result
    API-->>Client: Verification response
